<PB REF="4" MS="y">
Volume which wholly con&s;i&s;ts of Ver&s;e, and the Treati&s;e of the <HI>Bathos</HI> placed in their &s;tead in This. The Reader may be a&s;&s;ured no other Edi|tion is either Genuine or Com|pleat, and that they are all the Things of this Kind which will ever be Printed by the &s;ame Hands.</P>
