<L>Italiam, <HI>fato</HI> profugus, Lavinaque venit</L>
<L>Litora: multum ille &amp; terris <HI>jactatus</HI> &amp; alto,</L>
<L>Vi &s;uperum&mdash;</L></Q>
<L>Arma Virumque cano, Trojae qui primus ab <HI>Aris</HI></L>
<L>Italiam, <HI>flatu</HI> profugus, <HI>Latinaque</HI> venit</L>
<L><PB N="98" REF="98">
Litora: multum ille &amp; terris <HI>vexatus,</HI> &amp; alto,</L>
